snippet.title: Raccoon Arrival - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming October 12, 2021, to PC: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1592990/Raccoon_Arrival/

Raccoon Arrival is a walking simulator and meditative puzzles game. Super emotional music across the colorful environment and deep story.

Visit the website to learn more: https://www.raccoonarrival.com/
